snippet.title: Fate/Samurai Remnant - DLC Vol. 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
AVAILABLE NOW:  

https://bit.ly/3TRY0uJ

Fate/Samurai Remnant DLC 2 "Record's Fragment: Yagyu Sword Chronicles" is  is now available on PlayStation®5, PlayStation®4, Nintendo Switch™, and Steam®.

The power of the Ritual swirling around Edo attracts many oddities.
Tsujigiri of tremendous skill. A mysterious deadly blade.
Investigating the situation, Miyamoto Iori comes face to face with Yagyu Munenori, a Rogue Saber.
